nodes.text: Kell Borean was a Human female patron of the Outlander Club on Coruscant, who was especially fond of the gaming tables. She was inside the Outlander Club when the Jedi Obi-Wan Kenobi and Anakin Skywalker were chasing Zam Wesell.
Borean wore a striking headpiece consisting of white and black fabric.
Kell Borean was played by Australian model and make-up artist Eliana Dona.
